extended KEI exists.  The caster must either have an extend item or spell casting reinforcement / mastery.<br>
<br>
i'll break it down for you:<br>
<br>
KEI:  duration w/ no focus or aa = 2 hours 30 minutes (150 mins)<br>
<br>
KEI + SCR(30%) = 3.25 hours (195 mins)<br>
<br>
KEI + SCRM(50%) = 3.75 hours (225 mins)<br>
