<br>
Being married irl to an enchantress and always benifiting from SC3 and 8th shawl = 50% buff I can attest to the variablity of extended KEI.<br>
<br>
There are a few reasons for this:<br>
<br>
1. All mage focus items give a % benifite that is up to and including the max not always max.<br>
<br>
Eg ID3/4 will not always give you a max damage nuke, it is up to 15% or what have you on the focus, no different with buffs.<br>
<br>
2. Some poeple have faster ticks than others due to lag, as a minstrell I do knowtice that 4 songs always land on me without dropping, but my wife in the next room, will only have 3 songs and with a passing bit of bad lag 2, information gets lost on the internet, and the sync of the server to client always favors the server not the client.<br>
<br>
3. Oddly it can take 10-15 minutes to log off even after you have logged, I have had GMR fade at different times, up to 10 minutes btw, after camping and logging at the exact same time, give a tick or two. Lag always hurts <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
So, if somone has all the fun SCM and the best focus, you can get a 0% extended kei if you just have bad luck with the roll on the extension.<br>
<br>
I do not know if this happens more with some focuses and less with others, but I have knowticed this as well.<br>
<br>
